media:group.media:title: Internet Archive 2022 Award Ceremony
media:group.media:description:
The Internet Archive presented the "Hero Award" to Carl Malamud on October 19, 2022 as part of their annual celebration.

A blog post is https://blog.archive.org/2022/10/19/2022-internet-archive-hero-award-carl-malamud/ and the video is at https://archive.org/details/internet.archive.2022-10-19.hero.award

This video is public domain. No rights reserved.
